## Component Architecture

### File Naming
- **Components:** `PascalCase` (e.g., `TranscriptView.tsx`, `RecordingControls.tsx`)
- **Hooks:** `camelCase` with `use` prefix (e.g., `useTranscription.ts`, `useRecording.ts`)
- **Utils:** `camelCase` (e.g., `formatTimestamp.ts`, `validatePath.ts`)
- **Types:** `PascalCase` (e.g., `types.ts` exports `Recording`, `TranscriptSegment`)

### Component Organization
```
components/
├── Recording/
│   ├── RecordingControls.tsx      # Start/stop buttons, status
│   ├── RecordingWaveform.tsx      # Live audio waveform visualization
│   ├── RecordingTimer.tsx         # Elapsed time display
│   └── index.ts                   # Barrel export
├── Transcript/
│   ├── TranscriptView.tsx         # Full transcript display
│   ├── TranscriptSegment.tsx      # Single segment (speaker + text + timestamp)
│   ├── TranscriptSearch.tsx       # In-transcript search
│   └── index.ts
└── ui/                            # shadcn/ui primitives
    ├── Button.tsx
    ├── Dialog.tsx
    ├── Input.tsx
    └── ...
```

### Barrel Exports
Each component folder has an `index.ts`:
```typescript
// components/Recording/index.ts
export { RecordingControls } from './RecordingControls'
export { RecordingWaveform } from './RecordingWaveform'
export { RecordingTimer } from './RecordingTimer'

// Usage elsewhere
import { RecordingControls, RecordingWaveform } from '@renderer/components/Recording'
```

