## Import Ordering

### Recommended Order
```typescript
// 1. External libraries (React, etc.)
import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react'
import { useTranslation } from 'react-i18next'

// 2. Internal components (via path aliases)
import { Button } from '@renderer/components/ui/Button'
import { useRecording } from '@renderer/contexts/RecordingContext'

// 3. Shared types
import type { Recording } from '@shared/types'

// 4. Utilities
import { formatTimestamp } from '@renderer/lib/formatTimestamp'

// 5. Styles (if any — rare with Tailwind)
import './RecordingView.css'
```

